      description:
        "> Human history is composed of significant historical events, and the past serves as a prelude. Today’s world has entered a turning point era once again. Global climate change, scientific and technological progress, and geopolitical influence are all happening at every moment, making the fate of human beings more closely linked together.\n>\n> What makes us curious is how to order such an entropy-increasing world, and the knowledge that these events contain in terms of time, causality, father-son, and correlation is an important resource for humanity. When we record it as it is, history is not a little girl to be dressed up. We do not want a centralized entity to control everything, making our history only opinions and no facts.\n>\n> Today, we begin anew, to build a history book written by the people and for the people.\n\n# UPTO3\nUPTO3 is an innovative **event knowledge graph protocol** designed to help users gain a deep understanding of and explore event data, and extract valuable information from it. It is based on the concept of an event knowledge graph, which constructs and utilizes event graphs to provide users with comprehensive and accurate event correlation information, thus supporting various intelligent applications and decision analysis.\n\n# Event Knowledge Graph\nIn the era of information explosion, people are faced with the challenge of dealing with massive amounts of event data. As an innovative data model, Event Knowledge Graph has become an important link connecting and sharing human events by organizing and representing events, entities, and relationships in a graphical form. It not only **helps us understand the correlations and influences between events**, but also **provides profound insights and decision support** support for decision-makers, scholars, and social researchers. However, building a comprehensive, accurate, and verifiable event knowledge graph has always been a huge challenge.\n\n![event knowledge graph](https://miro.medium.com/v2/resize:fit:720/format:webp/1*zzJPbX4M44YEGe9TpwL27Q.png)\n\n# Vision\nOur vision is to build a globally shared and verifiable human event knowledge graph by establishing a consensus-based blockchain protocol. We deeply understand the value and significance of event knowledge graph for human society, and therefore are dedicated to addressing the challenges of event extraction, verification, and correlation to provide a trusted event knowledge platform for the global community.\n\n\n## Components of the UPTO3 Protocol\n1. Event Elements\n2. Publisher Role\n3. Validator Role\n4. Event Validation\n5. Reward Mechanism\n\nFollowing the philosophy of Web3, UPTO3 builds **a decentralized and user-driven event knowledge graph platform. It realizes user participation and autonomy, protects data privacy, adopts open protocols and trustless interactions**, and reduces the involvement of intermediaries. \n\nBy combining artificial intelligence and blockchain-based technology, UPTO3 provides an innovative solution for constructing a reliable and high-quality event knowledge graph.\n\nYou can read more information [here](https://medium.com/@upto3/upto3-building-a-web3-protocol-for-human-event-knowledge-graphs-91da541e3cc0).\n",
