      description:
        "PolyCoach is a dApp built on Polygon that helps you use the 21-days rule to train good habits through Web3 style. We refer to the famous 21-day habit-building theory and practice it through smart contracts on the chain.\n\nYou can create an exclusive Coach on the Polygon mainnet to train a good habit by depositing a certain amount of tokens into the Coach contract and continuously withdrawing these tokens during 21 consecutive check-ins and earn $COACH token.\n\nThe current Web3 social products are too utilitarian, which makes most users use them for the potential wealth opportunities behind them. This further makes Web3 Social Dapp more financial. It is divorced from the communication and fun of social products. This makes the accumulated data useless and boring.\n\nWe believe that the mass adoption of Web3 social is based on the accumulation of real data from more real users. We are focusing on this, by exploring interesting online social scenes, so that more valuable data can be deposited in web3.\n\nTherefore, you will find that PolyCoach, a small toy with social interaction attributes and easy operation, will attract real users to use the product for non-utilitarian purposes. We will understand a user's life goals in a decentralized way, and obtain the progress of his efforts and other users' evaluations of him. PolyCoach is our first step. We will focus on allowing more and more dimensions of user data to be deposited in the Web3 environment and become the flywheel of Web3 Social.\n",
