        "# Project Overview\nSUPRNTRL is a community-driven NFT collection built on the Sei network, focused on story-building and exploring onchain culture. Our collection aspires to create a club of on-chain natives on and beyond Sei. Inspired by the worlds of anime and manga, SUPRNTRL consists of 6,969 AI-assisted artworks, each with varying levels of rarity.\n\nArtwork by: @kunalzedd\n\nOur project emphasizes several key initiatives to drive growth and engagement within the Sei ecosystem:\n\n- ### Story-Driven NFTs:\nSUPRNTRL NFTs are more than just collectibles; they are integral pieces of a larger, evolving narrative shaped by the community.\n- ### Sei Story Builders:\nBy launching on Sei, the network becomes a core element of the SUPRNTRL narrative, reflecting our commitment to building on this platform.\n- ### Engineered Capital:\nA Telegram group composed of key individuals within the Sei network, designed to foster increased collaboration and strengthen ties within the Sei community.\n\n- ### Sei Builders Spaces\nWeekly Spaces to bring together Sei V2 builders\n\n---\nSUPRNTRL is committed to creating a unique and immersive world inspired by anime and manga on the Sei network. Through creativity, collaboration, and community engagement, we aim to build a thriving ecosystem that celebrates the art and culture of Sei.",
