      description:
        "# 🌐💰 datalatte: Tokenize and monetize data! Revolutionize market research and ethical Ai. 🚀🔐\n\ndatalatte is a dApp empowering people to anonymize, tokenize, and monetize their data! We're on a mission to transform market research, promote ethical Ai, and bridge the economic gap by enabling users to monetize their digital footprint securely and fairly. \n\n**Our Vision**: A transparent data economy where people have control over their data and the freedom to choose what to do with it.\n\n**Our Mission**: Empowering internet users to monetize their data, while providing researchers and organizations with survey-based insights to develop and improve their products.\n\n**Our Values**: Community & Collaboration, Transparency & Integrity, Leadership & Innovation, Equality & Equity.\n\n## 🎯 Gitcoin Beta Round Milestone: Decentralized & Permissionless Survey Protocol\n\nFor this Gitcoin beta round, we aim to build a permissionless and decentralized protocol for survey publishers. This will enable:\n\n1. Survey publishers to create surveys and create rewards.\n2. Users to participate in surveys, earn incentives, and tokenize & monetize their data anonymously.\n3. Researchers and organizations to access valuable survey-based insights through a decentralized data marketplace e.g ocean protocol’s data marketplace.\n\nTo achieve this milestone, we will leverage Ocean Protocol's dataNFT smart contracts and build an open-source protocol for anyone to use and verify the transparency of our dApp.\n\n## 🚀 Join Us on Our Journey to Transform Data Ownership & Monetization!\n\nDatalatte aims to create a more equitable and transparent system for data monetization by empowering individuals and providing researchers and small businesses with access to valuable data. By supporting our Gitcoin grant, you're helping to build a future where data is not exploited but recognized as the property of individuals.\n\n# We show you how to manage and monetize your data 🌐🔐💰\n\n**We greatly appreciate your contributions and support! Let's build a fair, ethical, and empowering data economy together! **🌟",
